## ğŸ§  Evolution: From Simple Chips to Intelligent Systems

What fascinates me most is how embedded systems have evolved:

ğŸ”¹ From simple 8-bit microcontrollers
ğŸ”¹ To ARM-based high-performance processors
ğŸ”¹ To AI-enabled edge devices

Todayâ€™s embedded systems can:

* Sense (via sensors)
